S No.127(I)
MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/1/2003-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 22n° December, 2003
1 Pausa, 1925(S).
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 21st December,
2003 :-
Shri T.R. Baalu relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
Environment and Forests; and
i)
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of Minister of
Environment and Forests.
ii)
Shri A. Raja relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
State in the Ministry of Health and Family Welfare.
iii)
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to Deputy Chairman and Members of the
Planning Commission.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary

Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
(P.'Gopalakrishnan)
Director (Cabinet)

Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
(P. Copalakrishnan)
Director (Cabinet)
